[
  {
    "text": "Whenever I talk to other people how to do Future Authoring writing plan",
    "begin": "00:00:00.220",
    "end": "00:00:03.200"
  },
  {
    "text": " Usually encounter delays",
    "begin": "00:00:03.320",
    "end": "00:00:04.500"
  },
  {
    "text": " This is not surprising",
    "begin": "00:00:04.680",
    "end": "00:00:05.480"
  },
  {
    "text": " Because it is already difficult",
    "begin": "00:00:05.660",
    "end": "00:00:06.700"
  },
  {
    "begin": "00:00:06.880",
    "end": "00:00:07.660"
  },
  {
    "text": " But the more problem is that they will think:",
    "begin": "00:00:07.660",
    "end": "00:00:08.620"
  },
  {
    "text": " \"I don't know how to start writing\"",
    "begin": "00:00:08.620",
    "end": "00:00:10.620"
  },
  {
    "text": " \"I will do a bad job\"",
    "begin": "00:00:10.800",
    "end": "00:00:12.340"
  },
  {
    "text": " \"I don't like this job\"",
    "begin": "00:00:12.440",
    "end": "00:00:14.220"
  },
  {
    "text": " \"I want to be perfect\"",
    "begin": "00:00:14.220",
    "end": "00:00:16.180"
  },
  {
    "text": " \"Wait until I have time to do it\"",
    "begin": "00:00:16.180",
    "end": "00:00:18.600"
  },
  {
    "text": " One reason you might not want to do it",
    "begin": "00:00:18.900",
    "end": "00:00:21.160"
  },
  {
    "text": " Not to mention there are five reasons",
    "begin": "00:00:21.220",
    "end": "00:00:23.440"
  },
  {
    "text": " So I suggest people",
    "begin": "00:00:23.440",
    "end": "00:00:25.080"
  },
  {
    "text": " Do something at will",
    "begin": "00:00:25.080",
    "end": "00:00:27.400"
  },
  {
    "text": " Even if there is only fragmentary time or a bad job",
    "begin": "00:00:27.900",
    "end": "00:00:30.720"
  },
  {
    "text": " Because you can do it",
    "begin": "00:00:31.200",
    "end": "00:00:32.980"
  },
  {
    "text": " I always tell my students when discussing master thesis with students",
    "begin": "00:00:33.140",
    "end": "00:00:36.160"
  },
  {
    "text": " Write a draft first, even if it is bad",
    "begin": "00:00:36.300",
    "end": "00:00:38.080"
  },
  {
    "text": " But we will have a short discussion first",
    "begin": "00:00:38.080",
    "end": "00:00:39.940"
  },
  {
    "text": " Because they don't think I really think like this",
    "begin": "00:00:39.940",
    "end": "00:00:42.000"
  },
  {
    "text": " Because that sounds cliché",
    "begin": "00:00:42.180",
    "end": "00:00:44.375"
  },
  {
    "text": " But not a cliché",
    "begin": "00:00:44.375",
    "end": "00:00:46.945"
  },
  {
    "text": " It's just like...",
    "begin": "00:00:46.945",
    "end": "00:00:48.240"
  },
  {
    "text": " You are a bad writer",
    "begin": "00:00:51.420",
    "end": "00:00:53.020"
  },
  {
    "text": " But if someone points a gun to your head and says:",
    "begin": "00:00:53.020",
    "end": "00:00:55.080"
  },
  {
    "text": " \"You must complete your hundreds of pages of draft by next Monday\"",
    "begin": "00:00:55.220",
    "end": "00:00:59.280"
  },
  {
    "text": " \"Otherwise I will blow your head\"",
    "begin": "00:00:59.280",
    "end": "00:01:00.660"
  },
  {
    "text": " \"I don't care how bad you write\"",
    "begin": "00:01:00.660",
    "end": "00:01:02.420"
  },
  {
    "text": " Then you will sit down and write obediently",
    "begin": "00:01:03.160",
    "end": "00:01:04.900"
  },
  {
    "text": " What i want to say is",
    "begin": "00:01:04.900",
    "end": "00:01:06.120"
  },
  {
    "text": " When you have a draft, you can modify it",
    "begin": "00:01:06.120",
    "end": "00:01:09.120"
  },
  {
    "text": " You can revise the draft repeatedly",
    "begin": "00:01:09.220",
    "end": "00:01:11.980"
  },
  {
    "text": " That's the most important and valuable and what you need",
    "begin": "00:01:11.980",
    "end": "00:01:14.220"
  },
  {
    "text": " You need a first draft of your own but not so good",
    "begin": "00:01:14.220",
    "end": "00:01:17.060"
  },
  {
    "text": " Jung has such a concept",
    "begin": "00:01:17.680",
    "end": "00:01:20.000"
  },
  {
    "text": " Developed from comedy",
    "begin": "00:01:20.100",
    "end": "00:01:22.860"
  },
  {
    "text": " Just",
    "begin": "00:01:22.860",
    "end": "00:01:24.240"
  },
  {
    "text": " \"The liar is the pioneer of the savior\"",
    "begin": "00:01:24.240",
    "end": "00:01:26.240"
  },
  {
    "begin": "00:01:26.240",
    "end": "00:01:26.940"
  },
  {
    "text": " This is one thing i learned from",
    "begin": "00:01:26.940",
    "end": "00:01:29.640"
  },
  {
    "text": " It sounds abnormal",
    "begin": "00:01:29.640",
    "end": "00:01:32.240"
  },
  {
    "text": " Hard to believe this is true",
    "begin": "00:01:32.280",
    "end": "00:01:34.360"
  },
  {
    "text": " The catastrophe clown fool in satire",
    "begin": "00:01:36.760",
    "end": "00:01:42.060"
  },
  {
    "text": " The fool is the pioneer of the savior",
    "begin": "00:01:42.140",
    "end": "00:01:44.940"
  },
  {
    "text": " why?",
    "begin": "00:01:44.940",
    "end": "00:01:45.660"
  },
  {
    "text": " Because you are a fool in a new field",
    "begin": "00:01:45.660",
    "end": "00:01:47.780"
  },
  {
    "text": " So if you don’t want to be a fool",
    "begin": "00:01:47.980",
    "end": "00:01:49.960"
  },
  {
    "text": " You can't start a new job",
    "begin": "00:01:49.960",
    "end": "00:01:51.460"
  },
  {
    "text": " You can't start a new job, you won't make progress",
    "begin": "00:01:51.540",
    "end": "00:01:53.380"
  },
  {
    "text": " and so",
    "begin": "00:01:53.380",
    "end": "00:01:54.140"
  },
  {
    "text": " Willing to be a fool",
    "begin": "00:01:54.140",
    "end": "00:01:55.620"
  },
  {
    "text": " There is a way to change",
    "begin": "00:01:55.720",
    "end": "00:01:57.660"
  },
  {
    "text": " This is also a kind of humility",
    "begin": "00:01:57.660",
    "end": "00:01:59.420"
  },
  {
    "text": " If you are about to start your life",
    "begin": "00:01:59.460",
    "end": "00:02:01.220"
  },
  {
    "text": " Your first job can be bad",
    "begin": "00:02:01.220",
    "end": "00:02:02.980"
  },
  {
    "text": " You will get smarter as you move forward",
    "begin": "00:02:02.980",
    "end": "00:02:05.580"
  },
  {
    "text": " This is the point",
    "begin": "00:02:05.580",
    "end": "00:02:07.060"
  },
  {
    "text": " Something attracted you that's what we are going to say today",
    "begin": "00:02:07.140",
    "end": "00:02:09.260"
  },
  {
    "text": " Maybe the stars that Geppetto is looking forward to are completely wrong",
    "begin": "00:02:09.480",
    "end": "00:02:13.580"
  },
  {
    "text": " But at least that's the stars",
    "begin": "00:02:13.580",
    "end": "00:02:15.020"
  },
  {
    "text": " At least it appeared",
    "begin": "00:02:15.020",
    "end": "00:02:17.000"
  },
  {
    "text": " At least it made him move forward",
    "begin": "00:02:17.000",
    "end": "00:02:19.540"
  },
  {
    "text": " So you say when you are attracted to something",
    "begin": "00:02:19.540",
    "end": "00:02:22.720"
  },
  {
    "text": " Or interested in something",
    "begin": "00:02:22.720",
    "end": "00:02:24.540"
  },
  {
    "text": " Then you start to think should I do this",
    "begin": "00:02:24.540",
    "end": "00:02:26.540"
  },
  {
    "text": " the answer is",
    "begin": "00:02:26.580",
    "end": "00:02:27.900"
  },
  {
    "text": " \"If I don't do it, there are other things I can do\"",
    "begin": "00:02:28.020",
    "end": "00:02:30.360"
  },
  {
    "text": " \"If it was a wrong decision?\"",
    "begin": "00:02:31.260",
    "end": "00:02:33.340"
  },
  {
    "text": " This is the wrong idea!",
    "begin": "00:02:33.340",
    "end": "00:02:34.200"
  },
  {
    "text": " Don't worry you don't know anything yet",
    "begin": "00:02:34.200",
    "end": "00:02:36.780"
  },
  {
    "text": " You are just about to take a difficult step, aren't you",
    "begin": "00:02:37.040",
    "end": "00:02:40.120"
  },
  {
    "text": " You have to move, you can’t stay where you are",
    "begin": "00:02:40.120",
    "end": "00:02:43.840"
  },
  {
    "text": " I have seen many people",
    "begin": "00:02:43.840",
    "end": "00:02:45.760"
  },
  {
    "text": " They said: \"I am 40 years old but I never knew what to do\"",
    "begin": "00:02:45.760",
    "end": "00:02:49.160"
  },
  {
    "text": " This is not a good phenomenon",
    "begin": "00:02:49.360",
    "end": "00:02:50.740"
  },
  {
    "text": " That's bad",
    "begin": "00:02:51.380",
    "end": "00:02:52.500"
  },
  {
    "text": " You might think",
    "begin": "00:02:52.860",
    "end": "00:02:54.340"
  },
  {
    "text": " There is a form of literature reminiscent of those who are very depressed",
    "begin": "00:02:54.340",
    "end": "00:02:57.940"
  },
  {
    "text": " When they remember the past",
    "begin": "00:02:57.945",
    "end": "00:03:00.785"
  },
  {
    "text": " About the things they didn't do",
    "begin": "00:03:00.945",
    "end": "00:03:03.965"
  },
  {
    "text": " And the mistakes they committed",
    "begin": "00:03:03.965",
    "end": "00:03:06.905"
  },
  {
    "text": " This is also worth thinking about",
    "begin": "00:03:06.905",
    "end": "00:03:09.880"
  },
  {
    "text": " There is a kind of compensatory error",
    "begin": "00:03:09.880",
    "end": "00:03:12.680"
  },
  {
    "text": " This is a compensation you try after you make a mistake",
    "begin": "00:03:12.680",
    "end": "00:03:16.120"
  },
  {
    "text": " Actually you think: Okay, I want to do this",
    "begin": "00:03:16.120",
    "end": "00:03:17.960"
  },
  {
    "text": " But you are not very good at making a lot of mistakes",
    "begin": "00:03:17.960",
    "end": "00:03:20.820"
  },
  {
    "text": " It’s like: \"What if I’m more focused?\"",
    "begin": "00:03:20.820",
    "end": "00:03:23.205"
  },
  {
    "text": " \"I shouldn't be this stupid anymore\"",
    "begin": "00:03:23.205",
    "end": "00:03:25.660"
  },
  {
    "text": " You can learn from the results",
    "begin": "00:03:25.660",
    "end": "00:03:29.060"
  },
  {
    "text": " and so",
    "begin": "00:03:29.060",
    "end": "00:03:30.780"
  },
  {
    "text": " You follow your desire",
    "begin": "00:03:31.280",
    "end": "00:03:34.600"
  },
  {
    "text": " But you were like a blind man at first",
    "begin": "00:03:34.720",
    "end": "00:03:37.060"
  },
  {
    "text": " You are not sure where the end is, you are afraid to move forward",
    "begin": "00:03:37.060",
    "end": "00:03:40.580"
  },
  {
    "text": " But you decide to step out",
    "begin": "00:03:40.580",
    "end": "00:03:43.960"
  },
  {
    "begin": "00:03:43.960",
    "end": "00:03:45.020"
  },
  {
    "text": " When you start to step out",
    "begin": "00:03:45.020",
    "end": "00:03:47.820"
  },
  {
    "text": " You can get shimmer and direction",
    "begin": "00:03:47.880",
    "end": "00:03:50.460"
  },
  {
    "text": " Because those past experiences will tell you",
    "begin": "00:03:50.460",
    "end": "00:03:53.175"
  },
  {
    "text": " When you push yourself out of the comfort zone",
    "begin": "00:03:53.180",
    "end": "00:03:57.100"
  },
  {
    "begin": "00:03:57.100",
    "end": "00:03:58.100"
  },
  {
    "text": " Then you find that the direction you are going is wrong",
    "begin": "00:03:58.105",
    "end": "00:04:01.425"
  },
  {
    "text": " Ten steps forward",
    "begin": "00:04:01.440",
    "end": "00:04:03.340"
  },
  {
    "text": " Then you think \"it doesn't seem to be here\"",
    "begin": "00:04:03.340",
    "end": "00:04:05.640"
  },
  {
    "text": " \"Not there, it should be here\"",
    "begin": "00:04:05.640",
    "end": "00:04:07.480"
  },
  {
    "text": " You found Liu Yinghua bright another village",
    "begin": "00:04:07.480",
    "end": "00:04:10.075"
  },
  {
    "begin": "00:04:10.080",
    "end": "00:04:11.220"
  },
  {
    "text": " You move on and you will find",
    "begin": "00:04:11.220",
    "end": "00:04:13.980"
  },
  {
    "text": " When you continue or change direction",
    "begin": "00:04:16.420",
    "end": "00:04:21.620"
  },
  {
    "begin": "00:04:21.620",
    "end": "00:04:22.120"
  },
  {
    "text": " Like in the Egyptian desert",
    "begin": "00:04:22.220",
    "end": "00:04:25.600"
  },
  {
    "text": " You find that the brilliance you seek is also moving",
    "begin": "00:04:25.600",
    "end": "00:04:29.020"
  },
  {
    "text": " It's not a permanent thing",
    "begin": "00:04:29.080",
    "end": "00:04:30.960"
  },
  {
    "text": " When you move toward it, it moves with it, and it leads you forward.",
    "begin": "00:04:30.960",
    "end": "00:04:34.040"
  },
  {
    "text": " You would say: Am I moving towards an ideal country?",
    "begin": "00:04:34.040",
    "end": "00:04:38.540"
  },
  {
    "text": " The answer is: no, you don't know anything",
    "begin": "00:04:38.600",
    "end": "00:04:41.340"
  },
  {
    "text": " Only know when you reach the goal",
    "begin": "00:04:41.520",
    "end": "00:04:44.000"
  },
  {
    "text": " But you might have that amazing glance",
    "begin": "00:04:44.000",
    "end": "00:04:45.920"
  },
  {
    "text": " When you continue",
    "begin": "00:04:46.220",
    "end": "00:04:49.100"
  },
  {
    "text": " You will become more and more aware",
    "begin": "00:04:49.300",
    "end": "00:04:52.640"
  },
  {
    "text": " And this will be a continuous process",
    "begin": "00:04:52.840",
    "end": "00:04:55.700"
  },
  {
    "begin": "00:04:55.800",
    "end": "00:04:57.380"
  },
  {
    "text": " Your move will look like this",
    "begin": "00:04:59.185",
    "end": "00:05:01.095"
  },
  {
    "text": " Interestingly",
    "begin": "00:05:02.920",
    "end": "00:05:04.360"
  },
  {
    "text": " All these transitions you face, the blow you face",
    "begin": "00:05:04.540",
    "end": "00:05:09.220"
  },
  {
    "text": " \"Gosh! I'm in trouble\"",
    "begin": "00:05:09.220",
    "end": "00:05:10.860"
  },
  {
    "text": " I seem to have died once, but recovered a little from it",
    "begin": "00:05:10.960",
    "end": "00:05:13.820"
  },
  {
    "text": " Like a phoenix on fire, reborn from every turn",
    "begin": "00:05:13.820",
    "end": "00:05:16.620"
  },
  {
    "text": " It's torture",
    "begin": "00:05:16.800",
    "end": "00:05:18.000"
  },
  {
    "text": " It's just like",
    "begin": "00:05:18.000",
    "end": "00:05:20.740"
  },
  {
    "text": " You have walked 20 miles",
    "begin": "00:05:20.740",
    "end": "00:05:24.400"
  },
  {
    "text": " But in fact you are only 3 miles ahead of your real goal",
    "begin": "00:05:24.400",
    "end": "00:05:27.140"
  },
  {
    "text": " Just 3 miles",
    "begin": "00:05:27.140",
    "end": "00:05:28.600"
  },
  {
    "begin": "00:05:29.000",
    "end": "00:05:31.920"
  },
  {
    "text": " When you are still in place, you are in a regressive state",
    "begin": "00:05:32.040",
    "end": "00:05:35.220"
  },
  {
    "text": " You can't stand still",
    "begin": "00:05:35.600",
    "end": "00:05:36.760"
  },
  {
    "text": " Because the whole world moves forward",
    "begin": "00:05:37.280",
    "end": "00:05:39.520"
  },
  {
    "text": " If you stand still, you will be left behind",
    "begin": "00:05:39.640",
    "end": "00:05:42.180"
  },
  {
    "text": " If you don’t move forward, you will only regress",
    "begin": "00:05:42.340",
    "end": "00:05:46.720"
  },
  {
    "begin": "00:05:46.720",
    "end": "00:05:47.220"
  },
  {
    "begin": "00:05:47.220",
    "end": "00:05:48.420"
  },
  {
    "begin": "00:05:48.960",
    "end": "00:05:49.960"
  },
  {
    "text": " And this is more in line with the Matthew effect:",
    "begin": "00:05:52.360",
    "end": "00:05:55.745"
  },
  {
    "text": " \"Those who have everything will be awarded more\"",
    "begin": "00:05:55.745",
    "end": "00:05:58.300"
  },
  {
    "text": " \"Take everything from those who have nothing\"",
    "begin": "00:05:58.440",
    "end": "00:06:01.500"
  },
  {
    "text": " This is a vigilance",
    "begin": "00:06:01.520",
    "end": "00:06:03.000"
  },
  {
    "text": " Don't stay where you are",
    "begin": "00:06:03.160",
    "end": "00:06:05.360"
  },
  {
    "text": " After you move forward hard",
    "begin": "00:06:08.040",
    "end": "00:06:10.300"
  },
  {
    "text": " Lessons learned at every turn",
    "begin": "00:06:10.900",
    "end": "00:06:14.920"
  },
  {
    "begin": "00:06:14.920",
    "end": "00:06:16.520"
  },
  {
    "text": " Then you stop making such fatal mistakes",
    "begin": "00:06:16.520",
    "end": "00:06:19.000"
  },
  {
    "text": " Maybe you will find a more suitable direction in the end if you can realize",
    "begin": "00:06:20.900",
    "end": "00:06:26.400"
  },
  {
    "text": " This will already be your journey although not yet",
    "begin": "00:06:26.400",
    "end": "00:06:28.560"
  },
  {
    "text": " May be worse than this",
    "begin": "00:06:28.560",
    "end": "00:06:29.300"
  },
  {
    "text": " Or some flaws",
    "begin": "00:06:29.300",
    "end": "00:06:32.700"
  },
  {
    "text": " But it doesn't matter",
